# Data Dictionary — park2023_disruptive

## Data source
Microsoft Academic Graph + USPTO + SciSciNet — Citation network 1945-2010
Access: public; Provenance: SciSciNet local

## Key variables
- Unit of analysis: paper
- Time window: 1945-2010
- Sample N: 469855
- Filter rules: require CD score, drop_na

## Indicator definitions
- Formula: CD5 = (Ni - Nj)/(Ni + Nj + Nk), 5-year window
- Parameters: 5-year citation window
- Computation steps: compute CD5 per paper, groupby year mean
